quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  22,6,"All this is because Allah, He is the Truth, and because He resurrects the dead, and because He has power over everything,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  22,7,"(all of which shows that) the Hour shall surely come to pass - in this there is no doubt - and Allah shall surely resurrect those that are in graves."{1},footnotes:1:1
  22,8,"And among people are those that wrangle about Allah without knowledge, without any true guidance, and without any scripture to enlighten them."{1}{2}{3}{4},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2,footnotes:3:3,footnotes:4:4
  22,9,"They wrangle arrogantly, intent on leading people astray from the Way of Allah. Such shall suffer disgrace in this world and We shall cause them to taste the chastisement of burning (in the Next)."{1},footnotes:1:1
  22,10,"That is the outcome of what your own hands have wrought, for Allah never wrongs His creatures."